我用Java 試做。<br />
<br />
version 1:  sort 左數字然後前後迫近<br />
<pre><code data-type="">    public int[] twoSum1(int[] nums, int target) {
        Element[] indexList = new Element[nums.length];
        for(int i=0;i&lt;nums.length;i++) indexList[i] = new Element(nums[i], i);
        Arrays.sort(indexList);
        int lower=0;
        int upper=nums.length-1;
        int sum = 0;
        while (lower&lt;upper) {
            sum = indexList[lower].num + indexList[upper].num;
            if (sum&lt;target) {
                lower++;
            } else if (sum&gt;target) {
                upper--;
            } else {
                break;
            }
        }
        if (sum==target) {
            int[] result = new int[2];
            result[0] = indexList[lower].index;
            result[1] = indexList[upper].index;
            return result;
        }
        else {
            return new int[2];            
        }
    }</code></pre><br />
<br />
唔算快，但係係我試到用最少記憶既做法<br />
<br />
version 2: brute force, 整個2-dim loop 狂試<br />
<br />
<pre><code data-type="">    public int[] twoSum2(int[] nums, int target) {
        for(int i=0;i&lt;nums.length;i++) {
            for(int j=0;j&lt;nums.length;j++) {
                if (i!=j &amp;&amp; nums[i]+nums[j]==target) {
                    int[] result = new int[2];
                    result[0] = i;
                    result[1] = j;
                    return result;
                }
            }            
        }
        return new int[2];
    }</code></pre><br />
<br />
呢個其實最快<img src="/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif" class="hkgmoji" /><img src="/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif" class="hkgmoji" /><img src="/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif" class="hkgmoji" />，但用多啲memory<br />
<br />
version 3: 按你既方法做，想法好有趣，我真係無諗過。不過要declare 一個hashMap，<br />
<br />
<pre><code data-type="">    public int[] twoSum3(int[] nums, int target) {
        HashMap&lt;Integer, Integer&gt; firstNumMap = new HashMap&lt;Integer, Integer&gt;();
        for(int i=0;i&lt;nums.length;i++) {
            Integer anotherNumIndex = firstNumMap.get(target-nums[i]);
            if (anotherNumIndex!=null) {
                int[] result = new int[2];
                result[0] = anotherNumIndex;
                result[1] = i;
                return result;
            } else {
                firstNumMap.put(nums[i],i);
            }
        }
        return new int[2];
    }
</code></pre><br />
<br />
唔係最快，但用最多memory.....<br />
<img src="https://na.cx/i/jnZ2PDc.png" data-thumbnail-src="https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjnZ2PDc.png&h=40980c31&s={SIZE}" /><br />
<br />
我覺得系統既test cases 唔夠大，令聰明既algorithm 發揮作用，最基本既手法反而最快。

